    "content": "-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n                             Dear future Husband- Meghan Trainor\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\nTabbed by: Tom\r\nE-mail: \r\n\r\nTuning: EADG\r\n\r\n[tab]This is just the notes played, for the rhythm listen to the song, it has a very similar rhythm to stand by\r\nme B.B king.\r\nTabs taken from TANAKA KENJI'S video\r\nCHORUS 1:\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-4-44- 4-43------------------1----3-4--(REPEAT)----------------------------|\r\nE|-----4------66-4-6-66-4-2-22---44------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]VERSE:\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---6---4\\0--(REPEAT)-------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|-4---4---------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]CHORUS 2 (CHANGES KEY):\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-5-55---5-54-----------------2----4-5--(REPEAT)----------------------------|\r\nE|-----5-------77-5-7-77-5-3-33--55------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n| /  slide up\r\n| \\  slide down\r\n| h  hammer-on\r\n| p  pull-off\r\n| ~  vibrato\r\n| +  harmonic\r\n| x  Mute note\r\n===============================================================================",
